OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTax rates to rise for      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhigher earners in Scotland 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Income tax rates for higher earners are
OL,6, expected to be increased in Scotland   
OL,7, for the next financial year.           
OL,9,FThe BBC understands the deputy first   
OL,10,Fminister, John Swinney, will announce  
OL,11,Fthe changes in his budget statement.   
OL,13,FHe is expected to put up the higher    
OL,14,Frate of tax from 41p to 42p in the     
OL,15,Fpound and to increase the top rate from
OL,16,F46p to 47p.                            
OL,18,FThe tax threshold for the top rate is  
OL,19,Falso expected to be lowered from       
OL,20,F#150,000 to closer to #125,000.        
